  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 : 6 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No need for all-party government : Country will return to normality within 6 months - Mahinda Amaraveera",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The current government in the country is an all-party government. So now there is no need for a new all-party government.",
        "Cabinet Co-Speaker Mahinda Amaraweera said that the Prime Minister will bring the country back to normal within the next 6 months.",
        "He therefore called on all parties to cooperate with the government instead of running after lust for power for narrow political purposes.",
        "During this, a question was raised regarding the Maha Sangh's insistence on forming an all-party government last week. While replying to this, Vijak Mahinda Amaraweera said the above.",
        "No matter what anyone says, the current government in the country is an all-party government. It cannot be said that it is not an all-party government because of the criticisms of a few. Even today we are inviting other parties.",
        "We request the government to cooperate. When Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe took office, several parties announced their cooperation through letters. Those who declared so should now give their cooperation.",
        "All people's representatives should think about the future of the country and take this responsibility.",
        "There must be a country for politics. Therefore, we call on everyone to come together and cooperate instead of working for narrow political purposes and running after the lust for power.",
        "It has only been 6 weeks since the new Prime Minister took office. The blackout which was observed for 8 hours that day has been limited to 3 hours today. Funds are saved for purchase of gas.",
        "So 6 months time should be given to this government. He said that the Prime Minister will bring the country back to normality by then."
      ],
